<br>
I had much more fun on the pickup raids as they posed more of a problem.<br>
<br>
The reason I did not enjoy the Guild raids is because my guild was way too powerful to be raiding this mob.  We had so many high levels there that they felt it was their responsibility to make sure us lowbies did not die and did all the work besides killing Naggy himself.  With all the high level buffs and insta rezes sitting around it was no challenge.  That made the raids no fun, I learned nothing from them except that level 65's can solo much of the stuff that a level 52 is scared of.<br>
<br>
